title: Prism video converter
description: Prism is a video file converter for Windows. It can convert video files from avi, mpg, vob, wmv, flv, 3gp and more into avi, 3gp, flv, mp4, mpg, asf or wmv files plus more. Prism Video Converter is very easy to use. Just add the files you want to convert to the list, select the format you want to use, and then click the convert button. Conversion to AVI and WMV continues to be free after 14 days. Version 1.20 is a bug fixing release.
